FRONT PAGE

HEADING: How does my council spend my money?
TEXT: We know that how your money is spent is important to you.
TEXT: At My Life My Council we have brought together information from councils across the country to show you where your money is going.

HEADING: Find my council
TEXT: Select from the options below to find out how your council spends money on what is important to you.

DISCLAIMER (Bottom of home page): 
Information used in this website is from the Local Authority Financial Statistics (LAFS) 30 June 2015 data set provided by Statistics New Zealand, and information on Council by Type and Council Contact Details held by the Department of Internal Affairs. All information is licensed for re-use under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International licence.



COMPARISON PAGE

DISCLAIMER: The graph shows how much each council is spending (as a percentage of the councils total operating expenditure) in different areas, compared to other similar councils (councils grouped by: Unitary, Regional, and Territorial authorities).


MY COUNCIL SPENDING PAGE

DISCLAIMER: The graph shows how much of an individuals council's spending (as a percentage of total operating expenditure) is being spent in different areas over time.


